{"tid":724110,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇機會係阿根廷足總比錢啲教練出阿甲仔","createTime":"2018-06-30T18:13:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-05T08:47:56.000Z","uid":5172,"like":67,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"c5a3a6392247af8664674b7db780ce6c327fcf17","tid":724110,"uid":5172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T18:13:17.000Z","msg":"唔止森柏奧利、之前幾個教練都會離奇出啲阿甲仔出嚟打正選，明明bench有好多一線球員。<br />\n淨係講今年世盃，係要出美沙？有咁多踢緊大會嘅唔出，係出班波都唔識控港超都未夠班踢嘅阿甲仔？<br />\n近年睇到阿根廷足總內部同貪腐問題都幾嚴重，有冇機會係阿根廷足總比錢啲教練又或者用啲手段逼教練出阿甲仔？<br />\n02世盃開始睇波，14年真係好可惜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，阿根廷今年個前線咁靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />未見到呢條鋒線真正發揮過應有水準真係好可惜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4aabbb4e1d94f550f0bcc0d7d052d5b26667df6d","tid":724110,"uid":5172,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T20:34:55.000Z","msg":"對住當今最強之一法國，咁多一線唔用都夾硬出啲阿甲仔，冇人覺得冇問題咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係似有黑幕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbf5d62dbb4d082150a053392e794ecd1d0ddcae","tid":724110,"uid":41434,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T20:37:50.000Z","msg":"錢可以解決既問題有美斯就解決到啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n只怪美沙屎忽太緊令光頭佬依依不捨<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23c094e355bed01639b681eb75bab52f1a5e5d45","tid":724110,"uid":8783,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T20:38:06.000Z","msg":"當打 大巴拿<br />\n連提高身價機會都冇<br />\n我想個阿根廷既全國點睇呢幾場波"},{"pid":"51280fa93ba3b6a8981ad30ca73766cdf1d47628","tid":724110,"uid":29080,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T20:39:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0210d1a73eeff5e1a84a3e91e00bd1b8ca424273","tid":724110,"uid":39708,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"